<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>38</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Twende kwa Yesu mimi nawe,
 Njia atwonya tuijue
 Imo Chuoni; na Mwenyewe,
 Hapa asema, Njoo!

[V2]
 Na furaha tutaiona,
 Mioyo ikitakata sana,
 Kwako, Mwokozi, kuonana,
 Na milele kukaa.

[V3]
 'Wana na waje', atwambia,
 Furahini mkisikia,
 Ndiye mfalme wetu pia,
 Na tumtii, Njoo.

[V4]
 Wangojeani? Leo yupo;
 Sikiza sana asemapo;
 Huruma zake zikwitapo,
 Ewe kijana, Njoo.</lyrics>
<title>Twende Kwa Yesu TZR38</title>
</song>